/na.cx/i/EMdRO5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEMdRO5B.jpg&h=012cf323&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求傳出去俾外國文宣巴絲打<br />\n<br />\n來源:<br />\n朋友Share出黎PDF <br />\n轉咗做圖方便大家"},{"pid":"000f9608808497ac159c0b500f83927688be802d","tid":1550823,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"自推(1/10)"},{"pid":"c4bce7146d91474cc73c284cef23b1ef74f451ab","tid":1550823,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"自推(2/10)"},{"pid":"c5a480c614de368d8f5f67256c7a109333d37598","tid":1550823,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:56:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1cf3ea1108bdc5b5ffd8df5e464fb3aa63f6066","tid":1550823,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:56:14.000Z","msg":"自推(3/10)"},{"pid":"a7d61aa7ab430435bba04b3dabb0e955f71845b2","tid":1550823,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:56:25.000Z","msg":"自推(4/10)"},{"pid":"c810167cc7d1d3007334def68d2da3e40c046f77","tid":1550823,"uid":160247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"試下中英都跟住唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"2d9d0df216e8bf77439baefb2a16faa6f588c2a7","tid":1550823,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:56:35.000Z","msg":"自推(5/10)"},{"pid":"5045fd9ea2188cd8c4f24eccdd0d92f0b473978f","tid":1550823,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:56:50.000Z","msg":"自推(6/10)"},{"pid":"bd7c39c461a95076e15a2dc1b0c892823a3fdd6b","tid":1550823,"uid":232167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:56:58.000Z","msg":"熱門一個908嘅post都冇？入嚟推兩野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1550800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1550800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c71230be04d497df303bfa7